# Exclude primitives-test from Turbo's default build pipeline
# This is a development/QA tool for testing CSS loading and bundle optimization
#
# To run primitives-test:
# - pnpm example:primitives (dev server)
# - pnpm example:primitives:build (production build)
# - pnpm example:primitives:analyze (bundle analysis)
# - pnpm --filter primitives-test dev
#
# This file ensures primitives-test is never included in:
# - pnpm build (only builds packages/*)
# - pnpm test (only tests packages/*)
# - pnpm lint (only lints packages/*)
*
